import React from 'react' import "./background_info.css" const Intro = () => { return (
Background Info The dashboard is an interactive tool for the analysis and intuitive visualization of the incentives for inc-dec gaming under different scenarios. Thereby, different mitigation strategies and two redispatch pricing mechanisms can be tested in a generator's dashboard and a load dashboard, representing the behaviour of the flexible generators or flexible loads.
) } export default Intro
